title: Pro Materials Exteriors
description: Pro Materials Exteriors is a complete package of professional and photorealistic shaders/materials for Unreal Engine, specially made for making exteriors.
longDescription:
Promotional Video


ProMaterials Exteriors is a complete package of professional and photorealistic shaders/materials for Unreal Engine, specially made for making exteriors. In this volume, the main theme is Urban Exteriors. 

  • All Assets, Models and Scenes are Included
  • RAW Renders (No post-production added)
  • Seamless Textures
  • No Tiling-Effect (too repetitive texture)
  • Learn How are made photorealistic shaders easily!
  • Complete PBR Maps Diffuse, Specular, Normal Maps, Dirt Alpha Maps and Decals.
  • Customizable Materials!
  • Pro Materials Interiors Demo Included Free!


Specially made for interiors!

  • Asphalt
  • Puddles
  • Wet Pavements
  • Concrete and Damaged Concretes
  • Bricks, Stone and Concrete Walls
  • Asphalt sign and Cracks Decals
  • And more
technicalDetails:
Texture Resolutions: (complete list)

  • 4096 (Diffuse Textures)
  • 2048 (Normal Texture and Speculars)
  • 1024 (Dirt Alphas)

Number of Materials:

  • 80 Master Materials
  • 24 Instanced Materials

Number of Textures: 128

Documentation (Complete Visual Guide Catalogue and User Manual): Download


Also check: Pro Grass
